A convenient top-loading disc system makes it a breeze to transition from "Call Me Maybe" to "November Rain." Use the included RCA-type A/V cables to connect the machine to almost any TV for high-quality audio and video output, ideal for channeling the full karaoke club experience right in your living room. Two microphone jacks allow you to serenade your cat with a riveting solo ballad or belt out a show-stopping duet with your bestie. Balance and echo control mean you always sound your best, and 54 LED disco lights keep the party atmosphere going all night long. The Singing Machine CDG Karaoke System SML385 includes a built-in speaker, wired microphone, AC adapter, RCA cables, sampler disc and instruction manual.</p>
